title: A New Beginning
text:
Jedi affiliation only.
Reaction: After you reveal 1 or more [Jedi] fate cards in your edge stack, remove all focus tokens from this objective.

title: Ahsoka Tano
text:
Elite.
Reaction: After you reveal 1 or more [Jedi] cards in your edge stack, draw 1 card. (Limit twice per turn.)

title: Ahsoka's Informant
text: Interrupt: When edge stacks are revealed, sacrifice this unit to place a [Jedi] card from your discard pile into your edge stack.

title: Ahsoka's Lightsabers
text:
Enhance a Force User or Force Sensitive unit.
Enhanced unit gains [Unit Damage] [Edge-Enabled Blast Damage].
Enhanced unit gains [Tactics] while it is participating in an engagement against a [Sith] objective.

title: Ancient Rivals
text: You may discard this card from your edge stack to discard a target [Sith] card or neutral non-fate card from your opponent's edge stack.

title: Ancient Rivals
text: You may discard this card from your edge stack to discard a target [Sith] card or neutral non-fate card from your opponent's edge stack.

title: Explosives Artist
text:
Influence.
Reaction: After this objective enters play, search the top 10 cards of your deck for a Specter unit, reveal it, and add it to your hand. Shuffle the remaining cards back into your deck.

title: Sabine Wren
text:
Action: Spend 1 resource to target a friendly unit. (Limit once per turn.) Until the end of the phase:
•if it is [Jedi], it gains [Unit Damage],
•if it is [Rebel Alliance], it gains [Tactics],
•if it is [Smugglers and Spies], it gains [Blast Damage]
•if it is a Specter unit, it gains edge (1).

title: Sabine's Armor
text:
Enhance a Character unit.
Enhanced unit gains +2 damage capacity.
If enhanced unit is Sabine Wren, she cannot be targeted by enemy card effects.

title: Custom Paint Job
text:
Enhance a card you control.
Enhanced card gains the [Jedi], [Rebel Alliance], and [Smuggler and Spies] affiliations.
While your opponent has 0 cards in hand, this enhancement gains: "Action: Draw 1 card. (Limit once per turn.)"

title: Improvised Explosive
text:
Enhance an objective.
Action: During an engagement against enhanced objective, sacrifice this enhancement to target up to 2 participating enemy units. Deal 1 damage to each targeted unit.

title: Well Equipped
text: Remove 1 token (any type) from a unit or objective card you control with 1 or more enhancements on it.

title: No Match for a Good Blaster
text: Reaction: After an enemy unit is destroyed during the resolution of a strike, deal 1 damage to the engaged objective. (Limit three times per phase.)

title: Han Solo
text:
Elite.
Targeted Strike.
Each other friendly [Smugglers and Spies] unit gains [Unit Damage].

title: Chewbacca
text:
Elite.
While this unit is committed to the Force, instead of counting Force icons during the Force struggle, each player counts the number of [Unit Damage] icons on ready units committed to the Force to determine who wins the Force struggle.

title: DL-44 Blaster Pistol
text:
Enhance a Character unit.
Enhanced unit gains [Unit Damage].
Interrupt: When enhanced [Smugglers and Spies] unit is targeted by an enemy card effect, shuffle this enhancement back into its owner's deck to cancel that effect.

title: Don't Get Cocky
text: Reaction: After you win an edge battle by 2 or more Force icons, a target participating unit gains [Blast Damage] [Blast Damage] until the end of the engagement.

title: Heat of Battle
text: Deal 1 damage to a target participating enemy unit.

title: There is No Conflict
text:
Sith affiliation only.
Reaction: After you reveal 1 or more [Sith] fate cards in your edge stack, place 1 focus token on a target enemy objective. (Limit 1 per turn.)

title: Darth Vader
text:
Elite.
Reaction: After a friendly fate card resolves, deal 1 damage to a target enemy unit. (Limit once per turn.)

title: 501st Commander
text: Reaction: After you lose an edge battle, remove this unit from the engagement to remove a target [Jedi] or neutral unit from the engagement. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Join Me
text:
Play only during your deployment phase.
Action: Take control of a target non-unique Character unit.

title: Ancient Rivals
text: You may discard this card from your edge stack to discard a target [Jedi] card or neutral non-fate card from your opponent's edge stack.

title: Ancient Rivals
text: You may discard this card from your edge stack to discard a target [Jedi] card or neutral non-fate card from your opponent's edge stack.

title: Heartless Tactics
text: Interrupt: When a [Scum and Villainy] objective you control with at least 1 captured card would be damaged, prevent 1 point of that damage. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Dengar
text:
Elite.
Reaction: After this unit is focused to strike, it gains X different combat icons of your choice until the end of the strike. X is the number of objectives you control with at least 1 captured card.

title: Security Operator
text: Reaction: After the conflict phase begins, move 1 captured card to a target objective you control.

title: Fortified Holding Cells
text:
Enhance a [Scum and Villainy] objective.
Enhanced objective gains +1 damage capacity and is considered to have 1 additional captured card.

title: Captured
text:
Play only during your turn.
Action: Capture a target enemy unit.

title: Preparation and Planning
text: Reduce the cost of the next event card you play this turn by 2.
